# Submission Notes

## What to include

- Screenshots of the required validation steps.
- GitHub repository link in the email body.
- Clear subject line using the course submission format.

## Screenshot checklist

- EC2 instance is running.
- Docker is installed successfully.
- `docker ps` shows the Nginx container.
- The Nginx welcome page opens in the browser.
- EC2 instance is terminated after cleanup.

## Best practice

- Keep screenshot names clear and consistent.
- Do not commit secrets or private keys.
- Keep the email short, professional, and friendly.
